{"tid":826715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯想不是「中國公司」　官方急急澄清","createTime":"2018-09-18T12:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T14:05:55.000Z","uid":8543,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a08adaee53c98679b8409800e3ad3f7140220996","tid":826715,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IMG_0484-770x439_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2FIMG_0484-770x439_c.jpg&h=1165a36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一間中國成立的公司，主席說並不是「中國公司」，實在政治不正確。英國傳媒日前訪問聯想主席楊元慶，以《聯想不是中國公司》為題作報道，結果官方要急急澄清。楊元慶在微博更稱，全球化過程中的 lost in translation 是一個長足的功課。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒《The Inquirer》上星期訪問楊元慶，問到為何當中興通訊、華為在美國業務受阻，聯想集團卻幾乎沒受到波及。他回應稱，聯想是一間全球公司，而非中國公司。這句被引作標題。<br />\n<br />\n報道刊出引發中國人爭議，聯想和楊元慶發聲明澄清。公司立場更指報道斷章取義、錯誤解讀。楊元慶則表示，自己的夢想是讓聯想不僅做成功的中國公司，更要做具有包容力的全球化公司。還指公司有七成員工來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/09/17/%e8%81%af%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%af%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8-%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9%e6%80%a5%e6%80%a5%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%2583%25b3%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2598%25af%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258f%25b8-%25e5%25ae%2598%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%2580%25a5%25e6%2580%25a5%25e6%25be%2584%25e6%25b8%2585%2F&d=d7Rm0k2e6ZO%2FYWbVS6sc9br9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=c5ca3ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/09/17/%e8%81%af%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%af%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8-%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9%e6%80%a5%e6%80%a5%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85/</a><br />\n<br />\n《The Inquirer》訪問楊元慶報道原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/3062798/lenovo-boss-were-not-a-chinese-company\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theinquirer.net%2Finquirer%2Fnews%2F3062798%2Flenovo-boss-were-not-a-chinese-company&d=d7Rm0k2e6ZO%2FYWbVS6sc9br9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=7539ef9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/3062798/lenovo-boss-were-not-a-chinese-company</a>"},{"pid":"778712ae2fe211c96574775c80b125a2d2da9c00","tid":826715,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"聯獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2caac7220be5fdfdd3c9221a068315de0b88018","tid":826715,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛(美)國"},{"pid":"ddaa93927b1cb026c2cc6d34b4b8b3db453b21c8","tid":826715,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"立刻道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fce9240c0d275a44d544cae26ccc103c0067c8","tid":826715,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"其實聯想從 IBM手上收購 Think 電腦品牌後，進軍台灣初期，曾經用「荷商思維（Think）」呢個名，<br />\n淡化品牌本身為大陸電腦企業品牌。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780b208fa3793b74dedd9b93343cef525e37f66d","tid":826715,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"以前共產黨就工人無祖國，依家就商人無祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57256ef8694b8c7e34bb0682d27388767ba619c","tid":826715,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"爛老母吔屎啦"}]}